  "source_notes": "Sy Scholfield downloaded a screenshot of Cox's natal chart shown in an interview between astrologer Chani Nicholas and Cox on YouTube (originally on Netflix) [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u-w-LVg1TGc]. The chart shows planets and Ascendant and MC in the signs (no degrees shown). The Ascendant is in about two-thirds Leo and the MC in mid-Taurus, and Nicholas comments that \"the asteroid Terpsichore was in a part of the sky that was rising up as you were born\" (in Cox's chart Terpsichore was at 22 Leo), and \"the Sun is in the 11th House\" (it is unclear which House system Nicholas has used).\\n\\nAt the start of a YouTube video \"It Got Better Featuring Laverne Cox\", Cox states \"I was born and raised in a city called Mobile, Alabama\", \"I was born seven minutes before my identical twin brother\" [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u-w-LVg1TGc].\\n",
